{"tid":406500,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家點睇法律？","createTime":"2017-09-19T16:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T00:45:00.000Z","uid":79735,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d33708aa9f118ac755fbc78dc5101e62c41ec1","tid":406500,"uid":79735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n細細個聽兩老講 其實法律係為左保護人而出現 就好似唔想有人濫權或官商勾結 剝削小市民嘅權利而出現<br />\n但最近同個fd傾個陣佢就話 人性根本就係萬惡 你如果唔畫明有咩做得有咩唔做得 天下一定大亂 所以法律係用黎好似管畜生咁樣管住d人 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 法律當然係保護人嘅權益啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保護權益只係呃細路嘅大話 人係需要好似畜生咁管"},{"pid":"dc1855f24b1de30b04291f277b24229c864aa7a9","tid":406500,"uid":79709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"有錢 有權 有地位 咪有法律"},{"pid":"e1180d4112e55209316166bb0139ea5943115a0f","tid":406500,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"法律係保護富豪同政治高層"},{"pid":"d8af9114f0358b7ddfb65a95ffeb3d62ef004b9e","tid":406500,"uid":136727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:38:53.000Z","msg":"法律面前，窮人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8431cfb4e9605c59deab8dc4c4256c5dfcf33bcf","tid":406500,"uid":124060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"少年你太年輕"},{"pid":"f8e46c3c80984a34a8fc7d10b4f82bdf16a4a793","tid":406500,"uid":79735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"咁大家做咩仲要反濫權嘅人<br />\n我地d窮人畜生黎炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d6eaa3ae92057b2e5607ec19eedd8e99d4a34","tid":406500,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:01:41.000Z","msg":"係有錢人既玩具<br />\n<br />\n淨係同你拖長黎玩你已經輸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再玩下程序"},{"pid":"a0329619af2596fb8c49c46c2a3475d686736e3d","tid":406500,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"法律有佢既限制"},{"pid":"fd9800122b62a8c5761d7f3f0e9657e29a9ad11c","tid":406500,"uid":71608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"人權好基於憲法，以美國為例人地，有10 amendments, 保障左好多自由，權利，佢既法例好自然就會base on此基礎上建立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而香港黎講，你幾唔鐘意中國都好，但一國兩制依樣嘢，就真係無得你唔接受，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啊爺就係介入香港政治，所以我地ff既港英憲法，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基本法啊真係無得繼續係喱個時局用得著。<br />\n<br />\n回應個問題，係為人民權利，利益，定一尾管人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會覺得兩樣俱全，但前者係行先。正如我所講，前者係好睇個地方憲法係米有所謂既人權保障........<span style=\"color: green;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喱到就真係多得共產黨政府唔少，我地香港人既憲法就算係寫到明保障乜叉嘢人權，共產黨屎忽痕，改下基本法，加個廿三條啊，又捉你煽動國家罪啊，咁就hihi 啦!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假如無左啲左膠香港政府，同埋共產黨介入，其實我地係有根有據，保障人權，就當學民領袖案，其實上訴到supreme court,係一定可以依據(如美國) 10 amendments所定既權利，反駁翻個charge 既條例。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有左喱啲legal system,真係會做到又保障人權，又管治既作用。<br />\n<br />\nconclusion: 屌，香港on99, 乜差都發展到一舊屎，以前電影文化金融都係Asia不知幾殺食，宜家，真係中國market 既金錢奴隸，咁真係啱哂啲左膠，左膠hi, 係講緊你啊，&ldquo;起來，做共產黨奴隸既人民&ldquo; woooooohooooooo! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Anyway, 聽日會繼續on99翻工，做個低調既港豬，一有時機移你老母民! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e12c10a7b97e574965ffe1c85f50097b08f452","tid":406500,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"有法可依-&gt;有法必依-&gt;以法限權-&gt;以法達義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce9c269265b92a75db90192f28ac8e88fd92d36","tid":406500,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法律面前，窮人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無法律既話窮人唔止含撚菊花點爆都得"},{"pid":"8c14f1a99643a0725c980bde232ecb0f915101cb","tid":406500,"uid":33883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T20:10:42.000Z","msg":"以前睇過o的討論法律o既書: rule of law同rule by law好似好大差別。97前香港肯定係rule of law; 97後就越o黎越似rule by law. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRule of Law =/= Rule by Law<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2F2010%2F02%2Frule_of_law%2F&d=99gpoQ9rwxAD6cIHe7IAgkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6e9332f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/</a>"},{"pid":"d83abc15706e8315c9cd257a77812bf4e09bd84a","tid":406500,"uid":146185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T21:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前睇過o的討論法律o既書: rule of law同rule by law好似好大差別。97前香港肯定係rule of law; 97後就越o黎越似rule by law. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRule of Law =/= Rule by Law<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2F2010%2F02%2Frule_of_law%2F&d=99gpoQ9rwxAD6cIHe7IAgkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6e9332f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/</a></blockquote><br />\nrule of law: the law is the king<br />\nrule by law: the king is the law"},{"pid":"1ad1f0fc276cb6cbe910f73a9c6d30f621b186b5","tid":406500,"uid":82125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T21:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前睇過o的討論法律o既書: rule of law同rule by law好似好大差別。97前香港肯定係rule of law; 97後就越o黎越似rule by law. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRule of Law =/= Rule by Law<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2F2010%2F02%2Frule_of_law%2F&d=99gpoQ9rwxAD6cIHe7IAgkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6e9332f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/</a></blockquote><br />\nrule of law: the law is the king<br />\nrule by law: the king is the law</blockquote><br />\n今日啱啱讀到呢兩樣野<br />\n<br />\nrule of law： 一切法律都係以保障人權，公民權益、自由行先<br />\n<br />\nrule by law: 用盡法律去保障當權者既利益"},{"pid":"e87bfa20085599b13e899defcfa0798f20b19616","tid":406500,"uid":82125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T21:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前睇過o的討論法律o既書: rule of law同rule by law好似好大差別。97前香港肯定係rule of law; 97後就越o黎越似rule by law. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRule of Law =/= Rule by Law<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2F2010%2F02%2Frule_of_law%2F&d=99gpoQ9rwxAD6cIHe7IAgkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6e9332f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boyangu.com/2010/02/rule_of_law/</a></blockquote><br />\nrule of law: the law is the king<br />\nrule by law: the king is the law</blockquote><br />\n今日啱啱讀到呢兩樣野<br />\n<br />\nrule of law： 一切法律都係以保障人權，公民權益、自由行先<br />\n<br />\nrule by law: 用盡法律去保障當權者既利益</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未出晒，所以支那成日強調 依法治國 依法辦事 梗係有原因啦，個13億支那豬都冇讀過書，聽落合理既野其實好撚on9,佢地都冇學識，高官講乜佢地聽乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dfdb4070106881d7552fd43545fe6ae399a8fb","tid":406500,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}